{"tid":1435973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軍事糾察（簡稱糾察，或稱警備糾察）是一種軍隊職務，大多負責糾舉部隊違紀人員，以肅軍風。","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:23:26.000Z","uid":48143,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80fece5f8e51c6ef05dd6a0ec81abda15cc46006","tid":1435973,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，你要做糾察既<br />\n就去最前線，mon撚住班狗，糾佢地老母察，唔係睇住示威者！<br />\n<br />\n示威者唔撚係聽你地指揮既人<br />\n你可以勸阻  但唔係制止<br />\n<br />\n就好似社工同左膠，還拖黑社會既時候你地可以勸喻，但唔好攔截！<br />\n<br />\n大家係要有共識，互相幫助，而唔係比自制組織控制！"},{"pid":"1cbdd478747a08c66fdb37b40f17d13cb61bc2c2","tid":1435973,"uid":212182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"no大台"},{"pid":"1d81eb7795fa9befe4fc1b96c99f6dfce9ae7b3a","tid":1435973,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"出機場和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eb5b7754083090cf629059f420ab8f79eb1c25","tid":1435973,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"狗察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1f023ba8dd69b0d47998f469614c0457159d86","tid":1435973,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189fdf7d8c7a317e70a004ef502ab8255fcae419","tid":1435973,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d81eb7795fa9befe4fc1b96c99f6dfce9ae7b3a","tid":1435973,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"出機場和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xu1Ydd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xu1Ydd.jpg&h=5bbdeed6&s=